main event: Royal Air Force jet fighters chased a mystery object over the English Channel on April 29, 1957, reported to be traveling at high speeds.
interesting points: The object was detected on radar flying at speeds in excess of 900 mph,The Royal Air Force scrambled jets to intercept the object,The chase occurred just before 9 o'clock at night,The object was initially reported to be traveling southeast over the Channel,An Air Ministry spokesman mentioned the possibility of the object being a manufactured item or natural phenomenon.
